Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Winter deepens recession
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wtsn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 21 Feb 1982
Reagan's proposed budget likely to be slashed by the House as economic crisis deepens. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less